videos.headline: Chandler punches it in for a Tennessee TD
videos.description: Ty Chandler scores from three yards out to open the scoring for Tennessee.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chandler punches it in for a Tennessee TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gray bursts through seam for 20-yard Tennessee TD
videos.description: Eric Gray jets through the Missouri defense and rolls into the end zone for the Tennessee score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gray bursts through seam for 20-yard Tennessee TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee's Gray takes quick pass for his second TD
videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano fires a quick pass to Eric Gray and the Tennessee RB scores for the second time against Missouri.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tennessee's Gray takes quick pass for his second TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gray's nice run sets up Guarantano's TD
videos.description: Eric Gray drops a defender with a nice cut, then Jarrett Guarantano pushes the pile forward for a two-yard TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gray's nice run sets up Guarantano's TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee stops Missouri momentum with INT
videos.description: Tennessee's Theo Jackson jumps the route and picks off Connor Bazelak's pass to end Missouri's drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tennessee stops Missouri momentum with INT) 2020/10/03 ESHEET
